Text.Value: インターネット インゲレスエリア３

Dialogue.Value: ほう････お前さん,なかなかダークな気を,発しているじゃねえか
どうだ 俺の育てたウィルスと,戦って 勝ったらダークチップを,くれてやるっていうのは
もちろん お前がベットするのは,その生命だがな････
俺のウィルスと戦うか？

Text.Value: やってやろうじゃない！,今は調子が悪い

Dialogue.Value: ちっ････怖気づいたか
よし じゃあ行くぜ！
ヒュ〜 勝ちやがったか！
よし こいつを受け取りな！
俺はお前に負けたんだ,これ以上とやかく言う,資格はねぇよ
[You’ve figured it out，this whole,place is just one big tourist trap.]
[If you want the real Engelles，,you’d be better off checking out,the UnderSquare.]
[Sure，it’s a bit dangerous，but,it’s authentic. Come with me，I’ll,keep you safe.... ehehe!]
[I went to the Square， but it’s all,shops and people trying to get,you to take their tours!]
[There’s not even any message,boards! Where are all the real,Engellians?]
[Heh.... the public Net might,be infested by kiddies， shills，,bootlickers，and tourists....]
[....but if you know the way，the,Net remembers who it belongs,to.]
[Yup，Engelles 3 patrol finished!,I’ve got a good enough view,of the area from here!]
[No need to check the rest of,the area，I’m sure everyone’s,being upstanding citizens!]
[I did some shopping at the,Square，but couldn’t find what,I wanted.]
[I thought there might be more,vendors out here，but it feels,like I took a wrong turn.]
[I think I’ll turn around.,I’m getting chills for some,reason，like I don’t belong....]
